Title: How can we open up safely when you can buy a vaccine certificate online for $200?

Title: New Math Book Rescues Landmark Topology Proof | Quanta Magazine
Description: Michael Freedman’s momentous 1981 proof of the four-dimensional Poincaré conjecture was on the verge of being lost. The editors of a new book are trying to save it.
